  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Icon Callout Box: Light Blue #E6F0F9 box, Brand Blue #00529b Nunito Sans 800 ~21px/28px left-aligned headline, white rounded-square badge with blue stroke icon half off left edge, left padding \u2265 half badge width + 24px, on white background."
